      • finish

        public void finish(int resultCode,
          android.os.Bundle results)
        Description copied from class: GoogleInstrumentation
        Ensures all activities launched in this instrumentation are finished before the instrumentation exits. Subclasses who override this method should do their finish processing and then call super.finish to invoke this logic. Not waiting for all activities to finish() before exiting can cause device wide instability.
        Overrides:
        finish in class GoogleInstrumentation
